Americans and Europeans expect their mediation mandate to end on 10 December.
The Russians, who had already blocked Kosovo's independence from the Security Council, insist on continuing negotiations beyond this end date.
Russia has been and will remain advocates of a negotiated solution, a mutually agreed solution, Botsane-Kharchenko said.
